{"tid":1462534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"檢討: 和理非行動一無大台就崩壞被騎劫","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:53:30.000Z","uid":4349,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6e22872ad4bc3c45a07f0624792d937f878046ee","tid":1462534,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"講左勁耐機場你和理非 和你飛, 和平舒服向國際宣揚香港既情況, 港共既暴力邪惡<br />\n<br />\n癱瘓機場只係一個bonus, 係政府驚出事自己搞到d遊客, 絕對唔係示威者主動要搞<br />\n機場係一個你唔帶頭搞衝突, 就一定和平無事既地方, 係一個同世界接軌既絕佳之地, 港共想搞鳩和理非都R爆哂頭<br />\n咁都可以比自己友(?)玩爛, 今日個畫面肉酸到<br />\n<br />\n個問題就係無大台, 太多自發抗爭, 佢地做錯都無人提, 一句兄弟爬山各自努力, 令成個方向四散, 失哂焦<br />\n<br />\n今日呢件事唔錯都錯左, 係一個好好既反省機會, 點樣可以唔失焦? 除左有大台係到統籌, 仲可以點? 大家要諗個方法"},{"pid":"5e9eabd359d0bd2f26dce882dea463267b44685e","tid":1462534,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db5d45e6ce979a470641b2a4477cada140779292","tid":1462534,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n建議集中火力搵出影響力最大嘅時間<br />\n睇下邊段時間最多人能響應，找出平衡<br />\n用隔日形式塞爆<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n隔日嘅好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"3eec69c4db5433079136430e7c5ea007053e75af","tid":1462534,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"811 721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316fe7a7cb85fb9e84d526816b48fa807c2beb78","tid":1462534,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"eb14056a4d6a28c2dd4b28394446372c4d655a8a","tid":1462534,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"咁現場有無人阻止個行動呢？？？"},{"pid":"cff50f20ac9fc8c8681a4722d9c3a9e45e1f0815","tid":1462534,"uid":4349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb14056a4d6a28c2dd4b28394446372c4d655a8a","tid":1462534,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"咁現場有無人阻止個行動呢？？？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"只見組隊去塞<br />\ntg谷亦有鼓吹, 叫人唔好塞就比人踢"},{"pid":"e9e2f6d81a0c2689181b7eec58317e39f20ea51d","tid":1462534,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5967af2e48616264a23150a214e8efc2f2544f54","tid":1462534,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cff50f20ac9fc8c8681a4722d9c3a9e45e1f0815","tid":1462534,"uid":4349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb14056a4d6a28c2dd4b28394446372c